---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Privacy Policy | Claim Guardians" 
  description="Privacy Policy for Claim Guardians LLC. Learn how we protect your data and privacy."
>
  <section class="section-white pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <span class="eyebrow" style="color:#00808C;">Legal Information</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-[#082142] mb-12">Privacy Policy</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-slate prose-lg lg:prose-xl font-medium text-slate-600 leading-relaxed space-y-8">
        <p><strong>Effective Date: March 19, 2026</strong></p>
        
        <p>At Claim Guardians LLC ("we," "us," or "our"), we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting the personal information you share with us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you visit our website or use our services.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#082142] pt-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect personal information such as your name, email address, phone number, and property details when you fill out a form or contact us for a free claim review. We also collect non-personal information through cookies to improve your browsing experience.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#082142] pt-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-3">
          <li>To provide and manage our services.</li>
          <li>To communicate with you regarding your insurance claim.</li>
          <li>To internal research and website optimization.</li>
          <li>To comply with legal obligations under Florida State Law.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#082142] pt-4">3. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure. We encourage you to contact us immediately if you suspect any unauthorized access to your data.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#082142] pt-4">4. Third-Party Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share data with trusted third-party service providers (e.g., forensic experts or contractors) only as necessary to handle your insurance claim or fulfill legal requirements.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#082142] pt-4">5. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
        <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Claim Guardians LLC</p>
        <p>304 Indian Trace Unit 655</p>
        <p>Weston, FL 33326</p>
        <p>Email: claims@claimguardians.com</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
